name: Chocolate Checkered Spade Handbag
description: This is a Chocolate Checkered Handbag with a Brown Spade Sewn on the front. It is lined with a Chocolate & Green Houndstooth print. It has a brown tote strap. It measures 12 inches wide and 13 inches tall.

name: Pink & Green Design Handbag
description: This cute Green, Pink, Yellow & White handbag is nice and roomy and perfect for all your essentials. It measures 13 1/2 inches wide and 13 1/2 inches tall. The total measurement of the strap is 27 1/2 inches. It is lined with the same fabric on the inside and is 100% cotton. Can be washed and laid flat to dry. Iron out any wrinkles.

name: Squirrel Tote
description: This is a squirrel tote bag. It is blue with a stripe of green going down the front. There is a cute blue squirrel stitched with green thread on the right side. It is lined with the same fabric on the inside. Very Sturdy!! This bag is perfect for school books, magazines, and even a purse if you carry alot! It measures 19 inches wide and 14 1/2 inches tall. It has a extra wide tote strap that you can put over your shoulder.
